And when you run the latest
version of the code on your device

21
00:01:07,820 --> 00:01:10,390
there should be any changes
in the appearance of the app.

22
00:01:10,390 --> 00:01:12,760
And remember you can check the logs
to verify that the list was

23
00:01:12,760 --> 00:01:13,840
created properly.

